msgid ""
"If you or someone you know needs help, you are not alone. These organizations provide free, "
"confidential support — no one will judge you."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du eller nogen, du kender, har brug for hjælp, er du ikke alene. Disse organisationer tilbyder "
"gratis, fortrolig støtte - ingen vil dømme dig."
